cdata.name: Solidified
cdata.desc:
Solidified is a smart contract security and development platform. Its main role is to act as a decentralized audit system and Bug Prediction Market. The platform intends to audit the users' smart contracts by following 4 main steps, multi-expert audit, fixes and verification, the bounty program and Bug Prediction Market (on early 2019). 

The Solid token is an Etherum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency developed by Solidified. The token can be used as a medium for purchase services within the platform.
